summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of that portion of the west 110 feet of Government Lot 2, Section 6, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W. M. lying east of Aurora Avenue, and between lines 132.78 feet and 396 feet south of North 80th Street, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-79 and 17-50, respectively.
